    public abstract class NumericValidatorAnnotator
extends gov.va.vinci.leo.ae.LeoBaseAnnotator
    Finds the numeric values covered by the input annotation types and then passes them to an abstract method for validation.

    Created by thomasginter on 9/1/15. updated by olga patterson on 6/14/2016
